One improvement for your service

Instead of:

FedexSubscriptionProjection projection =
        repository.findSubscriptionDetails(...)
        .orElse(null);

if (projection == null) {
   return null;
}

Use:

return repository.findSubscriptionDetails(
                customerId,
                accountNumber)
        .map(this::mapToResponse)
        .orElse(null);

Cleaner and easier to test.


